NAME

MojoX::Model - model for Mojolicious (Catalyst::Model-like)

DESCRIPTION

This is a Mojolicious model.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc
command.

    perldoc MojoX::Model

You can also look for information at:

    Repository
        http://github.com/dionys/mojox-model
    Bug tracker
        http://github.com/dionys/mojox-model/issues

AUTHOR

Denis Ibaev, dionys@cpan.org.

